        <abstract> 
<p>Mentioned to Appleton only that stereotypes [for <hi rend="italic">Insectivorous plants</hi>] would be provided for "a little above cost price". Glad the price of the book will be 14s. He likes making money, but cares more for wider distribution of his books. Is uneasy about sale of <hi rend="italic">Insectivorous plants</hi>.</p> 
